%% BPMN-like process (represented with flowchart)
flowchart LR
    User((User)) -->|Request| APIGateway[API Gateway]
    APIGateway --> AuthService
    AuthService -->|valid| BookService[Booking Service]
    BookService --> CheckAvailability{Available?}
    CheckAvailability -- Yes --> Reserve[Reserve Slot]
    Reserve --> PaymentGateway
    PaymentGateway -->|success| Confirm[Confirm Booking]
    Confirm --> Notify[Notify User]
    CheckAvailability -- No --> Reject[Reject Request]
